            "image": "shopify://shop_images/F29_Commuter_E-Bike_page_1500W.jpg",
            "image_pos": "left",
            "title": "<p>48V 10Ah Battery</p>",
            "content": "<p>The PostJoy F29 features a 48V 10Ah battery designed to support everyday commuting, errands, and longer city rides without frequent charging. With high-capacity power on board, you can ride farther and spend less time worrying about your next charge.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
