          }
        },
        "item_Y77eFc": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/F29_Commuter_E-Bike_page_free_basket.jpg",
            "image_pos": "right",
            "title": "<p>Added Utility at No Extra Cost</p>",
            "content": "<p>The PostJoy F29 includes a front basket and rear rack at no extra cost, adding practical cargo space without the need to purchase extra accessories.Carry groceries, backpacks, work essentials, deliveries, and everyday gear with ease on daily commutes or weekend errands.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_yxmgJc": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/F29_Commuter_E-Bike_page_1500W2.jpg",
            "image_pos": "left",
            "title": "<p>1500W Peak Motor</p>",
            "content": "<p>The PostJoy F29 is powered by a 1500W motor, 30N.M and reaches speeds of up to 25 MPH, giving you smooth acceleration and efficient performance for daily commuting. Whether you're riding to work, running errands, or cruising through city streets, the F29 helps you move faster with less effort.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_4A6yqg": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/F29_Commuter_E-Bike_page_tire.jpg",
            "image_pos": "right",
            "title": "<p>26\" x 2.0\" Commuter Tires</p>",
            "content": "<p>The F29 rides on 26\" x 2.0\" tires, offering a balanced feel for paved roads, bike lanes, neighborhood streets, and daily commuting routes.<br/>The city-ready tire size helps deliver smooth rolling efficiency, stable handling, and a natural riding feel.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_qBUgpX": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/F29_Commuter_E-Bike_page_tire.jpg",
            "image_pos": "left",
            "title": "<p>Front Suspension Fork</p>",
            "content": "<p>The front suspension fork helps absorb road vibration and small bumps, making everyday rides smoother and more comfortable. From uneven pavement to neighborhood roads, the F29 helps reduce harsh impacts so you can ride with more confidence.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
